title: What is F-Droid, SideQuest, Lynx Manager and SideLoading in general for Lynx R1 ?
description:
I explored what is F-Droid and needed to make a video recap a bit what it is and how it works. This video is playthrough of all the way to sideload and the difference between the software and way to do it. A bit technical and raw. But the aim is to give information while I create workshop later on the topic.
